d = {}
for origin in origins:
    dataframe_name = str(origin).lower()
    dataframe_name = dataframe_name.replace(" ","_")
    dataframe_name = dataframe_name.replace(".","_")
    dataframe_name = dataframe_name.replace("","o")
    dataframe_name = dataframe_name.replace("","g")
    dataframe_name = dataframe_name.replace("","c")
    dataframe_name = dataframe_name.replace("","u")
    dataframe_name = dataframe_name.replace("","s")    
    print(dataframe_name)
    d[dataframe_name] = pd.DataFrame(table1[table1['Country-name']==origin])
